# The photo/link scanner calls the Anthropic API server-side (Vite dev middleware
# at /api/scan). Provide a key here (copy this file to .env) or log in with the
# `ant` CLI. Without credentials, the scanner falls back to manual entry.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the scan endpoint (defaults to /api/scan). Point this at a
# deployed serverless function when hosting the PWA.
# VITE_SCAN_ENDPOINT=/api/scan
